<ul><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/FireEmblemFates" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/FireEmblemFates">Fire Emblem Fates</a></em> has <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigBrotherMentor" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigBrotherMentor">Xander</a> mention a variant of this when giving advice to his son <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PrincelyYoungMan" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PrincelyYoungMan">Siegbert</a>. He apparently still suffers from nerves in front of crowds. So how does he get past this?
<div class="indent">"...Bunnies. Whenever the people's beseeching eyes caused me to lose my nerve... I would imagine them as bunnies. Even the most chickenhearted, after all, never shrank from a bunny's stare."
