<h2 class="bold font-l">I Am a Little Weirdo</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
King thinks Gus is going to suggest he do something like &quot;Imagine everyone in their underwear&quot; to help him overcome his stage fright, but Gus thinks that's gross. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="yanptj" data-video-descrip="Squidward tries to imagine Squilliam in his underwear, but he turns out HOT." data-video-title="Oh no, he's hot!" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/yanptj_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/yanptj.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/ImagineTheAudienceNaked" data-video-tropename="Imagine the Audience Naked" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/SpongeBobSquarePants" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/yanptj.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Oh no, he's hot!</span></p>
</a>
</div>
